text: Iain Thomas RankinDistrict 47: Timberlea-Prospect cbc.ca (born April 9, 1983) is a Canadian politician. He is the 29th and current premier of Nova Scotia since February 23, 2021. He is a member of the Nova Scotia House of Assembly for the Nova Scotia Liberal Party, representing the electoral district of Timberlea-Prospect. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1983 births Category:Premiers of Nova Scotia
title: Iain Rankin (politician)
